  "details": "Easy to Moderate"
}

{
  "day": "7",
  "heading": "Trek from Arram Pathri to Aru. Drive to Srinagar",
  "sub_heading": "Trek Distance: 8.20 km | Trek Duration: 6 hours | Altitude Loss: 11,854 ft to 7960 ft",
  "details": "Easy. You are expected to reach Srinagar by 8.00 PM. Cost will be Rs 3,000 per cab (5-6 Seater).\nPlease note: The distance between campsites may vary by 100 meters depending the weather conditions and the route you take. The altitude may also vary by 100 feet for similar reasons."
